{quote}(A) would be available only to the root account on the host, which I think is sufficient. {quote}
It may work if it is just POC. What if we put it into production? Not all users are root or in root group, right? Do we need some work here? May be not in docker level.
Docker changes pretty fast, we need to make sure we do not need to make corresponding changes on Hadoop side once Docker has changes.

